data.description: Welcome to your tranquil oasis in Hillsborough! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath home is nestled by a picturesque pond, offering serene water views just a stone's throw away from the convenience of International Dr. It's only a short 10-minute drive to the delightful town of Conway and a quick jaunt to the beautiful beaches of the area.  As you approach, you'll be greeted by the inviting front porch, perfect for sipping your morning coffee or unwinding with an afternoon nap. Step inside, and you'll find a well-appointed interior featuring granite countertops and stainless steel appliances in the kitchen, vaulted ceilings that create an open and airy atmosphere, and ample closet space to keep your home organized.  But the true gem of this property is the screened porch that overlooks the peaceful pond. Whether you're watching the sunset or simply enjoying the soothing sounds of nature, this space is sure to become your favorite retreat.  Hillsborough offers a wealth of community amenities, including a playground for the kids, a pickleball court for some friendly competition, and a refreshing pool to cool off on those warm summer days.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home. Schedule a visit today and experience the tranquility and convenience that this Hillsborough gem has to offer. HVAC replaced Aug 2023.
